        Joint decay-chain analysis : LLNL physicists on the ring : Физики LLNL в кольце

    section Feb 2004
        Phys. Rev. C 69, 021601(R) : JINR + LLNL co-authorship : Соавторство ОИЯИ + LLNL
        Publication in open literature : No classification : Без грифа секретности

